<li><a href="http://www.philaprintshop.com/images/kurzpaceo.jpg" class="external text" title="http://www.philaprintshop.com/images/kurzpaceo.jpg" rel="nofollow">"Battle of Paceo", 1899 painting by Kurz and Allison</a></li>
