log Republic"><i>Katagalugan</i> (Sacay)</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Moro_Rebellion" title="Moro Rebellion">Moro Rebellion</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <i>Epilogue:</i> <a href="/wiki/Jones_Law_(Philippines)" title="Jones Law (Philippines)">Philippine Autonomy Act of 1916</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tydings-McDuffie_Act" title="Tydings-McDuffie Act">Philippine Independence Act</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Commonwealth_of_the_Philippines" title="Commonwealth of the Philippines">Commonwealth of the Philippines</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Treaty_of_Manila_(1946)" title="Treaty of Manila (1946)">Treaty of Manila</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Philippines" title="Philippines">Republic of the Philippines</a></div>
